 American Rapper, DaBaby Arrested for Gun Possession. Source (Instagram/@dababy) American Rapper DaBaby was arrested Thursday in Beverly Hills for possession of a loaded and concealed firearm. It was reported that the security at the Gucci store on Rodeo Drive called the Beverly Hills Police Department claiming that one person in a group of men was carrying a firearm in his waistband. Before the rapper and the group he was with left the area, police made contact with DaBaby, searched the vehicle, and found a concealed and loaded handgun.